@startuml labReportBody-map-cs
hide circle
hide stereotype
hide members
hide methods
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam class {
BackgroundColor<<LogicalModel>> #APPLICATION
BackgroundColor<<Profile>> #TECHNOLOGY
}
legend right
| <#APPLICATION>  Logický model |
| <#TECHNOLOGY>  Profil |
endlegend
